{"title":"New Norco Sight VLT CX eMTB is 20% Lighter with Bigger Battery & Further eBike Range","link":"https://bikerumor.com/new-norco-sight-vlt-cx-emtb-is-20-lighter-with-bigger-battery-further-ebike-range/","date":1743598800000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Norco)\" /></p>\n<p>The news out of British Columbia, Canada, today is that <a href=\"https://www.norco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Norco</a> finally launches their all-new Sight VLT CX eMTB, expanding on their MTB line of bikes. We got a sneak peek at the new eMTB <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/norco-sight-vlt-cx-emtb/\" target=\"_blank\">already back in October</a>, but now it’s out and ready to hit the trail.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This revamped Sight VLT CX is 20% lighter than <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/norco-sight-vlt-29-looms-extra-large-for-2020-with-big-wheels-and-range-extender/\" target=\"_blank\">the previous generation</a>. Plus, it also comes with a larger 800Wh internal battery and benefits from the significantly reduced riding noise of the lastest Bosch powertain. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Norco’s eMTB Line-up Expands with the New Sight VLT CX</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"693\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289-297x161.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289-120x65.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-first-pic-e1743552466289-768x416.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos / Norco)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Norco says that all of this is done without compromising the full-power eMTB experience. Their new Sight VLT CX is about balance and boosting the rider’s confidence.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Product Manager, Paul Burnett, had this to say, “<em>Reducing the weight of the Sight VLT was a major goal for us. The combination of weight reduction, VPSHP suspension, balanced geometry, Ride Aligned, and the Bosch CX drive system makes the Sight VLT CX the complete, full-power eMTB package</em>.”</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>New Bosch Performance Line CX eMTB powertrain</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB motor closeup\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup-768x511.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-motor-closeup-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Powered by the latest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/boschs-new-performance-cx-ebike-motor-is-not-more-powerful-but-is-better-and-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">4th generation Bosch Performance Line CX </a>drive system, the Sight VLT CX is lighter, quieter, and more responsive than before. The Bosch motor delivers 85Nm of torque. And, with the bigger Bosch PowerTube 800Wh battery, it’s ideal for long days. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use the Norco x Bosch Flow app to fine tune the assistance levels, and motor/battery range.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB cockpit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cockpit-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB drive side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-drive-side-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like with all of the full-suspension mountain bikes in their line, Norco used its rider-first philosophy when designing the Sight VLT CX ebike. Norco’s “industry-leading” Ride Aligned Setup Guide is about creating the best rider experience. And the Sight VLT CX is no exception.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB cx motor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cx-motor-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Norco riders can adjust their bike fit and suspension tune on the fly. They can also save different setups for different ride and trail styles. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB rocky\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-rocky-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB straight down\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-straight-down-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Combine this with the Bosch Flow app and you can dial in every ride to just how you like it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"855\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB C1\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1-768x513.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C1-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Sight VLT CX C1</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3-.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3-.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB C3\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3-.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C3--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>The Sight VLT CX C3</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB C2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-C2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Sight VLT CX  C2</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Sight VLT CX is available in three different models – Sight VLT CX <a href=\"https://www.norco.com/bikes/e-mountain/e-all-mountain/sight-vlt-cx/25-sight-vlt-cx-c1/\" target=\"_blank\">C1</a>, <a href=\"https://www.norco.com/bikes/e-mountain/e-all-mountain/sight-vlt-cx/25-sight-vlt-cx-c2/\" target=\"_blank\">C2</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.norco.com/bikes/e-mountain/e-all-mountain/sight-vlt-cx/25-sight-vlt-cx-c3/\" target=\"_blank\">C3</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>All share the same carbon frame, 160mm of fork travel, and 150mm of rear wheel travel using a high-pivot suspension layout with an enlosed idler pulley. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>All models also come as a mixed-wheel mullet setup.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sight VLT CX geometry</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://www.norco.com/cmsb/uploads/bikes/series/my25-sight-vlt-cx-geometry-drawing-opt.svg\" alt=\"Sight VLT CX Gen 4 (NEW)\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><table><thead><tr><th><br />Wheel Size</th><th>29″/27.5″</th><th>29″/27.5″</th><th>29″/27.5″</th><th>29″/27.5″</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td></td><td>Travel (mm front/mm rear)</td><td>160/150</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Reach</td><td>447.5</td><td>472.5</td><td>497.5</td><td>522.5</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Stack</td><td>627</td><td>636</td><td>645</td><td>654</td></tr><tr><td>HTA</td><td>Head Tube Angle</td><td>64</td></tr><tr><td>OS</td><td>Fork Offset</td><td>44</td></tr><tr><td>ST</td><td>Seat Tube Length</td><td>395</td><td>415</td><td>445</td><td>475</td></tr><tr><td>STA</td><td>Effective Seat Tube Angle</td><td>77.25</td><td>77.5</td><td>77.75</td><td>78</td></tr><tr><td>RC</td><td>Rear Centre Length</td><td>432</td><td>436</td><td>440</td><td>444</td></tr><tr><td>RC</td><td>Rear Centre Length at Sag</td><td>441</td><td>445</td><td>449</td><td>453</td></tr><tr><td>BB</td><td>Bottom Bracket Drop</td><td>25/5</td></tr><tr><td>BBH</td><td>Bottom Bracket Height</td><td>349</td></tr><tr><td>HTT</td><td>Horizontal Top Tube</td><td>589</td><td>613</td><td>637</td><td>661</td></tr><tr><td>WB</td><td>Wheelbase</td><td>1222</td><td>1255</td><td>1289</td><td>1322</td></tr><tr><td>SOH</td><td>Standover</td><td>701</td><td>711</td><td>714</td><td>729</td></tr><tr><td>HT</td><td>Head Tube Length</td><td>115</td><td>125</td><td>135</td><td>145</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Trail</td><td>133</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Recommended Seatpost Drop</td><td>150</td><td>170</td><td>200</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Maximum Post Insertion</td><td>250</td><td>270</td><td>300</td><td>330</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Stem Length</td><td>40</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Crank Length</td><td>165</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Tire Size</td><td>2.35″ – 2.6″</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Water Bottle Compatible</td><td>1 x 620 mL</td><td>1 x 750 mL</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering.webp\" alt=\"Norco's New Sight VLT CX eMTB cornering\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Norcos-New-Sight-VLT-CX-eMTB-cornering-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the link below for pricing and build specs. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.norco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Norco.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-norco-sight-vlt-cx-emtb-is-20-lighter-with-bigger-battery-further-ebike-range/\">New Norco Sight VLT CX eMTB is 20% Lighter with Bigger Battery &amp; Further eBike Range</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"c842caae9595e2d718b51b35ccf33ad869f77c613b204335ce1448665f5bfd7f","category":"Cycling"}